{"TopicId":183253,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Autostruts gone?","CreatedByName":"Reinhart Mk.1","CreatedById":194521,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-30T00:09:06Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Reinhart Mk.1","CreatedById":194521,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-30T00:09:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I got bored and started a new game and after finding out how insanely useful autostruts were... well that\u0027s the first thing I enabled. But while in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E I don\u0027t see the option to use them. All I see is \u0022rigid attachment\u0022. Help?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022xPMQmQd.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/xPMQmQd.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-30T00:22:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cs\u003EAdvanced Tweakables needs to be enabled in your difficulty settings.\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nScratch that.\u00A0 You must have that on already for Rigid attachment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAutostruts will become available when you unlock the actual strut in the tech tree.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-03-30T00:23:06Z\u0022 title=\u002203/30/2019 12:23  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 30, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Geonovast\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Reinhart Mk.1","CreatedById":194521,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-30T00:29:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223571699\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022183253\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221553905337\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAutostruts will become available when you unlock the actual strut in the tech tree.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTHANK YOU, this was driving me nuts!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}